<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.9.5">
<l>nantāneṭu narakattiṭai naṇukāvakai nāḷum</l>
<l>entāyeṉa vimaiyōrtoḻu tēttumiṭa meṟinīrc</l>
<l>centāmarai malarumciṟu puliyūrccala cayaṉat</l>
<l>tantāmarai yaṭiyāyuṉa taṭiyēṟkaruḷ puriyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You of lovely lotus[-like] feet on a watery bed in Ciṟupuliyūr,</l>
<l>Where red lotuses bloom in the surging waters, the place where</l>
<l>Unblinking [celestials] praise you, worshipping daily,</l>
<l rend="indent">as they call, “My Father,”</l>
<l>Graciously grant to me, your servant, the means</l>
<l rend="indent">that [I] not go into imperishable vast hell.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
